{
  "stem": "1736.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I had forgotten all about that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It just came back to me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The whole thing was that we knew we had to be on the lookout all the time.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- but, of course, you can ask me is, well, why did you stay there?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I can't answer that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I haven't got the, you know, the-- if I would have been rational, if I would've been older, and later on I did get to that, I would have said, well, let's get out of here.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I suppose economic situations, all that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I can't-- I can't tell you that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we had no long discussions, no, no, no.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, I mean, we concerned ourselves with the moment of what we were going to do, or what we did the day before, and all this sort of thing.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were no political discussions, or, you know, elaborate discussions with those boys.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He would tell me what they did at camp, and different things, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he would tell you what--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, yes, he'd sort of tell me, we did this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We did that, you know, and I would listen to him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He didn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I remember other occasions.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember the rise of-- of the Hitler regime.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One of the reasons being that Dessau was a city where the Junkers factory was.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Junkers was the factory that manufactured a very well-known brand of airplanes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You might have-- you may remember there was a plane called Stuka, which is, in German, [GERMAN] bomber.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's a dive bomber.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I remember Hitler arriving there one day to initiate some-- some new plane or something like that.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To Dessau, and seeing that whole parade of people, and seeing him standing in his--",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
